後端改變會馬上反應到前端(大概?)

架設步驟

1.首先，确保你已经安装了 Django 和 Django Channels。
pip install django channels

2.配置 Django Channels
INSTALLED_APPS = [
    ...
    'channels',
    'myapp',
]

ASGI_APPLICATION = 'myproject.asgi.application'
CHANNEL_LAYERS = {
    "default": {
        "BACKEND": "channels.layers.InMemoryChannelLayer"
    }
}
